<html lang="en">

<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./assets/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./assets/css/animation.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./assets/css/w3.css">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <link rel="icon" href="./assets/JRC.png">
</head>

<body style="{{this.backgroundStyle}}">
    {{{navigation}}}
    <div id="container">
        <div id="flexContainer">
            <div class="flexBox" style="margin:5px;width: 60%; min-width: 700px;">
                <div class="w3-card-4">

                    <header class="w3-container w3-blue">
                        <h1>Welcome to JRC Season 10</h1>
                    </header>

                    <div class="w3-container w3-light-grey">
                        <p>The season is underway - 8 rounds of rally action to determine the winning drivers and teams.</p>

                        <p><strong>New drivers</strong></p>
                        <p>Mid season joins are not permitted in season 10. Be sure to register your interest for season 11 and monitor the discord for information about placements.
                        In the meantime enjoy our side series rallies detailed below - available to join for any driver.</p>

                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="w3-card-4">

                    <header class="w3-container w3-blue">
                        <h1>Other JRC events</h1>
                    </header>

                    <div class="w3-container w3-light-grey">
                        <p><strong>Side Series</strong></p>
                        <p>JRC runs a number of side series including Historic and Themed that run almost continuously and are open to all</p>
                        <p>See our discord for more info, and check the results in the side series results links section below</p>

                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="w3-card-4">

                    <header class="w3-container w3-blue">
                        <h1>Season 10 Calendar</h1>
                    </header>

                    <div class="w3-container w3-light-grey" style="font-weight: bold;">
                        <img style="max-width:100%; margin:auto; display:block;" src="./assets/S10_calendar.png" />
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="flexBox" style="margin:5px;">
                <h2>Rulebooks</h2>
                <h3>Season 9</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><a
                            href="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/679708933434114093/869233980950589461/JRC_Season_10_Preliminary_Rulebook_v2.pdf">Rulebook</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h2>Side series results links</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="./themed/index.html">Themed</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="./historic/index.html">Historic</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="./endurance/index.html">Endurance</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="./modern/index.html">Modern</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Other links</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://junior-rally-championship.fandom.com/wiki/Junior_Rally_Championship_Wiki">The Wiki</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <!--
        DROPDOWN
    -->
    <script>
        function openNav() {
            var x = document.getElementById("mobileNav");
            if (x.className.indexOf("w3-show") == -1) {
                x.className += " w3-show";
            } else {
                x.className = x.className.replace(" w3-show", "");
            }
        }
    </script>
    <!--
        BACKGROUND ANIMATION
    -->
    {{#unless this.backgroundStyle}}
        <div id="particles-js"></div>
        <script src="http://cdn.jsdelivr.net/particles.js/2.0.0/particles.min.js"></script>
        <script src="./assets/particleConfig.js"></script>
    {{/unless}}
</body>

</html>